{"tid":319112,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[Jupas] 究竟HKU BBA(IS)出路如何","createTime":"2017-07-12T14:24:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-06T12:58:37.000Z","uid":60247,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"389b7bfc3932dcd4a9a68098e17afb9e98c5b36d","tid":319112,"uid":60247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:24:50.000Z","msg":"睇網上評價好似好兩極，有啲就話有programming skill + business唔難搵工甚至幾吃香，但係又有人話係19BBA中伏科，搞到我1516，都唔知擺唔擺上A1好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打可以指點下迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b154aa9c8cc752b4473a4e24656e0d1cd95b9c0b","tid":319112,"uid":28820,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好亂黎<br />\n睇你咁問 你應該對BBA唔同major都唔係好認識<br />\nIS其實好濕尻 你學嘅programming/IT knowledge只係好basic 絕對唔好aim話出黎好似cs咁勁 除非你自己個底好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你只不過係take多vba/data base management嘅course 唔代表你可以變成IT奇才<br />\n如果你想讀BBA但唔知興趣起邊 你最好入school based收生嘅bba<br />\n好似CUHK Ibba or HKUST business and management<br />\nUST可以讀一年之後先簡major 起碼你知道晒所有major有咩唔同 同埋自己興趣係咩 到時你覺得對IS有興趣先入都未遲<br />\nCU就好似冇major但可以簡concentration 即係讀多啲你prefer嘅area<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 小心啲簡 唔好好似我咁尻簡左 hku a&amp;f 入到去先發現對account完全無興趣"},{"pid":"dc083c5f7bc0569cdf8ec12c8781192365ca79e6","tid":319112,"uid":7851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-12T17:24:50.000Z","msg":"諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e2c57fe5ad1aca468becc6dd9d9e170468552a9","tid":319112,"uid":11323,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:51:49.000Z","msg":"HKU IS同其他u唔同 你一定要double major IS同CS 如果你唔想讀programming 淨係想讀IS可以早抖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  同埋呢科係可以讀5年拎埋BEng major in Computer Science 咁多間u IS黎講hku算幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21915f8f31632a563656d61b780c1f0b6fa3f219","tid":319112,"uid":11323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T00:55:40.000Z","msg":"至於出路方面 當然你可以做code狗 但有d人會入銀行做IT 又或者去consultancy firm例如accenture做consultant 甚至Business analyst 所以出路唔會太差既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8e7cced267b1cf7de949a0703e929af9ef00b7","tid":319112,"uid":111504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:39:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇網上評價好似好兩極，有啲就話有programming skill + business唔難搵工甚至幾吃香，但係又有人話係19BBA中伏科，搞到我1516，都唔知擺唔擺上A1好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有無巴打可以指點下迷津<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n同cs唔同既係is以用家角度黎諗，其中一個目標係通過cs既技能提升business方面既效率<br />\n所以唔會學到好專<br />\n但係都有同學cs好勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁當然啦首先你要同時唔討厭cs同business <br />\n因為入到去發覺自己其中一方面讀唔掂係超難trans科<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過前景目前望落去都唔錯，讀五年兩個degree好值得諗呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8a8dd783158b71f1aab8a805927ced059c5f012","tid":319112,"uid":111504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-13T19:40:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n讀緊hku bbais  <br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cee556510990c8b310857401dc70808effe40ca","tid":319112,"uid":11323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T01:51:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n讀緊hku bbais  <br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYear幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c5c883efb0ca8815f1b5af7d19340a7a80d3ff4","tid":319112,"uid":111504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T03:04:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n讀緊hku bbais  <br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nYear幾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪要相認啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e4bf18664921c2ecc8ecc2af42fd1d2713dcc00","tid":319112,"uid":60247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-14T18:30:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n讀緊hku bbais  <br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你讀緊又覺得依科點?會唔會好chur? <br />\n同埋你點評價前景(唔hea讀嘅話)"},{"pid":"dce058eac86966732ec1ccf87597bdd66df941bd","tid":319112,"uid":111504,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T03:21:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>諗住a1攞hku bba is 或者cu ibba <br />\n都係十五十六<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n <br />\n讀緊hku bbais  <br />\n睇下幫唔幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打你讀緊又覺得依科點?會唔會好chur? <br />\n同埋你點評價前景(唔hea讀嘅話)</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nChur真係因人而異<br />\n因為有人做曬大學5件事都唔覺得chur<br />\n有人起身返9半都覺得chur<br />\n重要既係心態<br />\n自己真係唔抗拒/有興趣先好揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n前景其實唔錯<br />\n雖然係咁見到有it狗比人炒<br />\n但係而家間間公司都講求創新同科技<br />\n所以一定同融合it同business有關<br />\n只要知道自己長處係邊度，is其實都幾抵玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efe5d3169876755de08bd404d73c28a7e6311f07","tid":319112,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T14:29:38.000Z","msg":"咪做business analyst"},{"pid":"e2a0780b94552f2fa96544c232f9bc9eed094c33","tid":319112,"uid":128399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-15T15:55:31.000Z","msg":"A2擺咗bbais 如果入咗各位巴打到時關照吓"},{"pid":"e4316246aceef42baa2da1f4b87c4c77202a11c7","tid":319112,"uid":60247,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-20T05:42:40.000Z","msg":"我4c2x 得27，擺咗係A1，啱啱好meet到佢嗰lq，希望入到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed99d673c16fcf5212718d3744e5cb58279abd4f","tid":319112,"uid":7851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-23T03:45:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我4c2x 得27，擺咗係A1，啱啱好meet到佢嗰lq，希望入到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴打有冇收到interview<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"8a0a48afb62ba36cd24f27c7124f4baf29a651c6","tid":319112,"uid":1283